flowchart TD
  UI[User intent] --> LR[Local repository mutation]
  LR --> SD[(SwiftData commit)]
  SD --> Q[PendingAction enqueue]
  Q --> W[Sync worker / explicit session sync]
  W --> R{Remote result}
  R -->|success| C[Mark completed and update sync metadata]
  R -->|transient| B[Increment attempt and retry later]
  R -->|permanent| F[Mark failed and surface recovery]
  R -->|conflict| P[Apply conflict policy]
  P --> REC[Reconcile local and remote]
